text: I spent a bit of time on the camera but I couldn't figure out a good way to make it work. I did try to guess at how one might implement it but I doubt it will work so I wouldn't get your hopes up. If it doesn't work and instead ends up causing problems in the code, just comment out everywhere with tensorflow stuff and maybe change the duck pickup to do a sweep by of the area since you would be more likely to pick it up that way than just driving to a random spot
